{"tid":2147743,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"Ipad/Android Tablet 上堂jot notes app 求推介","createTime":"2020-08-09T12:33:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-16T14:11:16.000Z","uid":336683,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"3d6b1d10652a8c023be240b2ae1bb98dc40472cc","tid":2147743,"uid":336683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T12:33:24.000Z","msg":"見好多人都係用notability / noteshelf<br />\n<br />\n有無ching係實際用過 或者有咩 <span class=\"red\"> 推介 </span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n請出招<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最好寫明an定ios app thx<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3f563469ed9d893f9e492673b175f4bdde56e4b","tid":2147743,"uid":112390,"like":0,"dislike":61,"score":-61,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T12:39:15.000Z","msg":"首先<br />\nnonju有自己嘅難處同彩數 <br />\n<br />\n如有得揀dse直入 邊個唔想<br />\n我都有努力過 我都試過每日訓4個鐘咁去溫書 操pp<br />\n咁我唔得即係唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有人鍾意男人 有人鍾意女人<br />\n各有取向<br />\n<br />\n有人適合DSE高壓模式一試定生死<br />\n有人適合HD/Asso持續考核GPA計分<br />\n各有自己選擇<br />\n<br />\n啲人覺得DSE考得差就一定係讀唔到書？一定唔應該入大學？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我就真係勸啲人睇多啲書 唔好坐井觀天、活在自己嘅世界<br />\n<br />\n同埋nonju入hku唔令我覺得羞恥 亦唔係後門狗 nonju入hku係光明正大寫喺hku個website<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n定係啲人覺得只有DSE jupas先係光明正大入HKU嘅唯一選擇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />lmao  <br />\n<br />\nnonju都用自己努力考gpa 一步一步升上去 <br />\n（定係你覺得讀嘅hd/asso畀完錢就乜都唔洗理gpa自己就會好似啲警察受武肺感染人數咁自動升升升）<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我唔係畀錢 唔係靠關係 光明正大咁用非DSE嘅方式入HKU 我就真係唔知啲人憑乜嘢講nonju係走後門<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實對比返我自己讀中學嘅經驗<br />\n讀完hd/asso嘅人 比起freshgrade嘅中學生<br />\n某程度上佢哋有更多嘅經驗喺接受全英嘅教學、寫paper &amp;reference （apa format）、group work合作、使用learn portal、應對freerider、睇百幾頁嘅ppt etc.（有錯望諒）<br />\n<br />\n大家雖然起點唔一樣 但最終都係為左讀大學 增長自己知識和技能 更好地融如社會 <br />\n未步入社會工作就已經要開始批鬥 分門別類 去區分前門後門 真係值得驕傲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而至於hall收唔收我 唔到我話 <br />\n咁我禮拜一就打去admission office問下nonju嘅學生入唔入到hku 嘅hall<br />\n<br />\n而你用你認知嘅HKU hall文化覺得佢哋未必收我<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">抑或可能係你<strong>坐井觀天</strong>呢？</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lightbulb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後同宜家讀緊hd/asso嘅人講聲<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 祝你來年過3爆4入到U"},{"pid":"691e4510e253b083a4e2364a24e11c54c1f476d5","tid":2147743,"uid":336683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T13:03:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b968633b06765d12eb176815e7379262eba71af8","tid":2147743,"uid":260113,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T13:12:56.000Z","msg":"iOS Notability"},{"pid":"e193f6824195a80b38e22aaadc7ef23672220295","tid":2147743,"uid":363621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b968633b06765d12eb176815e7379262eba71af8","tid":2147743,"uid":260113,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T13:12:56.000Z","msg":"iOS Notability"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T13:20:45.000Z","msg":"Notability +1<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n用埋pdf expert睇readings"},{"pid":"04fc52a0fa9397e75512b21d61e2e94619627ce6","tid":2147743,"uid":34525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T13:35:50.000Z","msg":"iOS 唔洗諗"},{"pid":"233ebe9212cd5282dc951ab30d6f5940cb3b4574","tid":2147743,"uid":34525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"04fc52a0fa9397e75512b21d61e2e94619627ce6","tid":2147743,"uid":34525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T13:35:50.000Z","msg":"iOS 